725164f-a.title: Queens: 27th Street - 49th Avenue
725164f-a.text:
27th Street, east side, south fron 49th Avenue to the Dutch
Eills, showing the Irving Iron Works at 50th Avenue. 27th Street
was formerly named Creek Street. The steel structure is for the
road to the 9Queens-Midtown Tunnel.
P. L. Sperr  July 27, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS
